<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8261554>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Adalia tetraspilota (Hope): a–i. elytral pattern variations; j. antenna; k. maxilla; l. epipleuron; m–o. male genitalia: m. tegmen, ventral view; n. tegmen, lateral view; o. penis; p. female, spermatheca." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8261554/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8261558>
    dc:description "FIGURE 16. Adalia tetraspilota (Hope): a. adult, dorsal view; b–e. male genitalia: b. tegmen, lateral view; c. tegmen, ventral view; d. penis; e. penis apex." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8261558/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8261560>
    dc:description "FIGURE 17. Adalia tetraspilota (Hope), life stages: a. eggs; b. single egg; c, d. early stage larva; e. full grown larva; f. pupa; g. adult, nominate form." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8261560/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

